CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 29, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Hello, Champ! - Sporting a trim moustache, Joe Louis is shown here with Frank Lavelle Jr., son of Frank Lavelle, Courier ad man, after he refereed a bout between Billy Conn and Al Patterson at the Dapper Dan show last week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boxer Joe Louis wearing Army uniform and holding Frank Lavelle Jr., with another boy on right, in living room
